title: Justin Bieber Poses With All 5 of His MTV EMAs After Breaking the Winning Record!
text: Justin Bieber poses with his awards in the press room at the 2015 MTV European Music Awards held at the Mediolanum Forum on Sunday (October 25) in Milan, Italy. The 21-year-old entertainer won Best Male, Best North American Act, Best Collaboration for “Where Are You Now?” with Skrillex and Diplo, Biggest Fans and Best Look [...] »
